data e kholo: Likhokahano tse kholo tsa data li kholo haholo hore li ka sebetsoa
ho ithuta ka mochini: Li-algorithms tse lumellang likhomphutha ho ithuta ho tsoa ho data
kerafo: Sebopeho sa li-node tse hokahaneng le mathoko
mongolo oa sephiri: Mekhoa ea puisano e sireletsehileng le ts'ireletso ea data
mochine oa sebele: Ketsiso ea software ea sistimi ea komporo
cloud computing: Ho fana ka litšebeletso tsa khomphutha inthaneteng
bohlale ba maiketsetso: E nolofalletsa mechini ho bonts'a boitšoaro bo bohlale
lit\u0161oant\u0161o tsa k'homphieutha: Ho theha le ho laola litšoantšo ka komporo
t\u0161ebelisano ea khomphutha ea batho: Boithuto ba hore na batho ba sebelisana joang le theknoloji
ts'ebetso ea puo ea tlhaho: Lik'homphieutha li utloisisa le ho sebetsana le puo ea batho
parallel computing: Ho sebelisa li-processor tse ngata ka nako e le 'ngoe ho rarolla mathata
khomphutha e ajoang: Ho hasanya komporo ho litsamaiso tse ngata ka marang-rang
software boenjiniere: Mokhoa oa ho rala, ho aha le ho hlokomela software
tshireletso ya tlhahisoleseding: Ho sireletsa litsamaiso tsa tlhahisoleseling ho tsoa ho phihlello e sa lumelloeng
ntshetsopele ya webo: Ho aha le ho hlokomela liwebsaete le lisebelisoa tsa marang-rang
ntshetsopele ya pele: Karolo ea basebelisi ba sebaka sa marang-rang ba sebelisana le eona
ntshetsopele ya morao-rao: Merero ea lehlakore la seva le taolo ea data ea sebaka sa marang-rang
nts'etsopele ea lipapali: Mokhoa oa ho etsa lipapali tsa video
ntshetsopele ya mehala: Ho theha lisebelisoa tsa li-smartphone le matlapa
mahlale a data: Ho fana ka lintlha le lintlha tsa bohlokoa
pono ea k'homphieutha: Ho nolofalletsa likhomphutha ho "bona" le ho utloisisa lintlha tse bonoang
nnete e ekeditsweng: Ho koahela tlhahisoleseling ea dijithale lefatšeng la 'nete
nnete ya sebele: Ho theha tikoloho e etsisoang e qoelisang
inthanete ea lintho: Netweke ea lisebelisoa tsa 'mele tse nang le bokhoni ba khomphutha bo kentsoeng
